{"article_id":"o9kN8SgTO1QBC8gg","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Jeff Sessions came to Capitol Hill in self-defense mode ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"refuting allegations","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that have dogged his short tenure as attorney general","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"about his role in the Russia imbroglio","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"plaguing the Trump administration .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"But there were few shockers in his Tuesday testimony before the Senate Intelligence Committee ,","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"as Sessions repeatedly shook off questions , particularly about his conversations with President Donald Trump .","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"Democrats were predictably displeased with his answers ,","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"but Republicans signaled","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"that they believe","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Sessions successfully cleared up any confusion","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"surrounding his own interactions last year with Russian officials .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"\" You 've answered questions","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"that surround the reasons of your recusal and the fact","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that you had never been briefed since Day One on the investigation , \"","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Sen. Richard Burr","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"( R-N.C. ) ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"the committee chairman ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"said at the end of the hearing .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"\" You made clear","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"that you ca n't think of any other conversations","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"that you 've had with Russian officials ...","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"just to name a few things","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"I think","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"you 've helped us to clear up . \"","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"The attorney general couldn ' t definitively recall","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"whether he interacted with Russian Ambassador Sergey Kislyak at an April 2016 forum at the Mayflower Hotel in Washington .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"He didn ' t recall","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"whether the president ' s son-in-law , Jared Kushner , had similar conversations with the Russian diplomat .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"And in a rapid-fire sequence of questions from Sen. Joe Manchin","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"( D-W.Va. ) ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Sessions repeatedly stressed","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that he could not recall","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"whether current and former White House officials such as Michael Flynn , Reince Priebus and Stephen Miller had met with Russian representatives during the 2016 campaign .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"The \" I don ' t recall \" line was a reliable response from the attorney general during the nearly three-hour grilling , particularly about one of the biggest questions","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"raised before his testimony","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"- whether he had further undisclosed meetings with Russian officials .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"Sign up here for Huddle","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"A daily play-by-play of congressional news in your inbox .","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"By signing up","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"\" I did not have any private meetings","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"- nor do I recall any conversations -","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"with any Russian officials at the Mayflower Hotel , \"","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Sessions said in his defiant opening remarks .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"Later , he slightly qualified his statement ,","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"acknowledging","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"that he \" may have had an encounter during the reception \" with Kislyak ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"but that was it .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"His responses prompted Sen. Kamala Harris","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"( D-Calif. )","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"to wonder","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"how much Sessions had prepared for his high-stakes hearing , perhaps with written documents , emails , notes or his personal calendar .","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"\" I attempted to refresh my recollection ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"but so much of this is in a wholesale campaign of extraordinary nature","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"that you 're moving so fast","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"that you do n't keep notes , \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Sessions explained .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"While Democrats were harsh toward Sessions ,","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"nearly all Republicans treated him gingerly .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"Sen. Tom Cotton","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"( R-Ark . )","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"was perhaps the most critical of Democrats ,","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"accusing them of tumbling \" down lots of other rabbit trails \"","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"because no evidence has surfaced so far of collusion between Moscow and Trump associates - a conversation","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that devolved into chatter about action movies .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"\" Have you ever , ever , in any of these fantastical situations , heard of a plot line so ridiculous","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"that a sitting United States senator and an ambassador of a foreign government colluded at an open setting with hundreds of other people","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"to pull off the greatest caper in the history of espionage ? \"","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Cotton mused .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"\" Thank you for saying that , Sen. Cotton .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"It 's just like through the looking glass , \"","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"Sessions responded .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"\" I mean ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"what is this ? \"","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Cotton was not alone","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"in running interference for Sessions .","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"Sen. Jim Risch","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"( R-Idaho )","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"noted","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"that senators regularly speak with ambassadors","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"and asked Sessions ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"\" Is that a fair statement ? \"","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"And Sen. James Lankford","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"( R-Okla. )","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"read a lengthy response from the Center for the National Interest ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"which hosted the April 2016 event at the Mayflower","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"it was unlikely that a private meeting between any two individuals could ' ve occurred","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"without drawing some attention .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"Lankford then asked Sessions :","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"\" Do you have any reason","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"to disagree with that ? \"","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"The support from Senate Republicans extended off the dais .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Sen. Luther Strange","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"( R-Ala. ) ,","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"who was appointed to Sessions ' Senate seat","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"and is now seeking to win it outright ,","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"attended most of the hearing","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"and issued a statement afterward ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"declaring","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"that the attorney general showed a \" complete commitment to integrity , transparency and the rule of law . \"","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"The still-new attorney general has had little practice at the witness table ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"and it showed","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"as he became rattled under questioning from Democrats","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"who have accused him of not being forthcoming about his interactions with Russian officials .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"His first eruption was directed at Sen. Ron Wyden","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"( D-Ore. ) ,","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"who pressed Sessions on what exactly fired FBI Director James Comey found so \" problematic \"","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"that he felt","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"the attorney general ' s recusal from the Russia probe was inevitable .","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"Comey had implied","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"there were reasons for the recusal","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"that had not been made public .","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"\" Why don ' t you tell me ? \"","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"Sessions retorted .","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"\" There are none , Sen. Wyden .","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"There are none .","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"I can tell you that for absolute certainty .","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"This is a secret innuendo","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"being leaked out there about me ,","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"and I don ' t appreciate it . \"","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"Wyden shot back :","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"\" You made your point","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"that you think","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"Mr. Comey is engaging in innuendo .","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"We ' re going to keep digging . \"","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"Later , Sessions admitted","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"that he was getting a bit flustered","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"as Democrats sped through a series of questions about his potential communications with anyone","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"connected to the Russian government .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"\" If I don ' t qualify ,","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"you ' ll accuse me of lying .","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"So I need to be correct as best","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"as I can , \"","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"Sessions ,","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"his voice rising quickly ,","depth":15},{"id":142,"text":"said","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"as Harris tried to cut off his answer","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"and move on to her next question .","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"\" I ' m not able to be rushed this fast .","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"It makes me nervous . \"","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"Sessions and Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein were testifying on Capitol Hill simultaneously Tuesday ,","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"but they weren ' t always in sync .","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"One such moment came","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"when Sessions testified","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"that Comey likely had an obligation to notify Congress","depth":16},{"id":152,"text":"when new evidence emerged in the probe into Hillary Clinton ' s State Department emails last October .","depth":16},{"id":153,"text":"\" Once the director first got involved and embroiled in a public discussion of this investigation ,","depth":18},{"id":154,"text":"which would have been better never to have been discussed publicly ,","depth":18},{"id":155,"text":"and said","depth":18},{"id":156,"text":"it was over ,","depth":18},{"id":157,"text":"then","depth":18},{"id":158,"text":"when he found new evidence","depth":19},{"id":159,"text":"that came up ,","depth":19},{"id":160,"text":"I think","depth":18},{"id":161,"text":"he probably was required to tell Congress","depth":19},{"id":162,"text":"that it was n't over ,","depth":20},{"id":163,"text":"that new evidence had been developed , \"","depth":20},{"id":164,"text":"the attorney general said .","depth":15},{"id":165,"text":"However , the letter","depth":17},{"id":166,"text":"Rosenstein wrote last month as part of the process","depth":18},{"id":167,"text":"of firing Comey","depth":18},{"id":168,"text":"indicated","depth":16},{"id":169,"text":"that the FBI director actually should have remained mum . \"","depth":15},{"id":170,"text":"Concerning his letter to the Congress on October 28 , 2016 ,","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"the Director cast his decision as a choice","depth":15},{"id":172,"text":"between whether he would ' speak ' about the decision","depth":17},{"id":173,"text":"to investigate the newly-discovered email messages","depth":17},{"id":174,"text":"or ' conceal ' it .","depth":16},{"id":175,"text":"' Conceal ' is a loaded term","depth":16},{"id":176,"text":"that misstates the issue , \"","depth":16},{"id":177,"text":"the deputy AG wrote .","depth":15},{"id":178,"text":"\" When federal agents and prosecutors quietly open a criminal investigation ,","depth":16},{"id":179,"text":"we are not concealing anything ;","depth":16},{"id":180,"text":"we are simply following the longstanding policy","depth":17},{"id":181,"text":"that we refrain from publicizing non-public information .","depth":17},{"id":182,"text":"In that context , silence is not concealment . \"","depth":16},{"id":183,"text":"Sessions had appeared to endorse Rosenstein ' s memo last month ,","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"so it was surprising that he took the opposite position at one point on Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"Sessions ' testimony also departed from Rosenstein ' s in a broader fashion ,","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"with the attorney general willing to discuss matters","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"special counsel Robert Mueller may be investigating","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"but his deputy declining to do so .","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"Sessions discussed his involvement in Comey ' s firing , something","depth":14},{"id":190,"text":"Rosenstein was not willing to do","depth":14},{"id":191,"text":"- citing the Mueller probe .","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"And the attorney general went even further :","depth":13},{"id":193,"text":"detailing his own interactions with the Russians as well as an Oval Office meeting","depth":14},{"id":194,"text":"that","depth":16},{"id":195,"text":"Comey said","depth":16},{"id":196,"text":"may have been part of an effort","depth":16},{"id":197,"text":"to obstruct the Russia investigation .","depth":16},{"id":198,"text":"Sessions clearly felt an urgency","depth":14},{"id":199,"text":"to speak","depth":14},{"id":200,"text":"in an effort","depth":14},{"id":201,"text":"to clear his name in the face of the \" false attacks \"","depth":15},{"id":202,"text":"he railed against Tuesday .","depth":15},{"id":203,"text":"He may also believe","depth":13},{"id":204,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":205,"text":"because he ' s recused from the Russia probe","depth":15},{"id":206,"text":"he is permitted to act more like a witness and less like a cautious Justice Department official .","depth":15},{"id":207,"text":"Much of Tuesday ' s hearing was devoted to Sessions ' refusal to answer certain questions","depth":9},{"id":208,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":209,"text":"he said","depth":11},{"id":210,"text":"endangered executive branch confidences ,","depth":10},{"id":211,"text":"but there were also the questions","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":"that were never asked .","depth":11},{"id":213,"text":"The most glaring :","depth":11},{"id":214,"text":"Did Sessions ever offer to resign due to Trump ' s dissatisfaction with his job performance ,","depth":13},{"id":215,"text":"as several news outlets have reported ?","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"The attorney general might have punted ,","depth":13},{"id":217,"text":"but his reaction might have betrayed the answer .","depth":13},{"id":218,"text":"Sessions was also never asked whether he did anything at all","depth":11},{"id":219,"text":"after Comey expressed discomfort with his interactions with the president .","depth":11},{"id":220,"text":"The attorney general generally rebuffed questions about his dealings with Trump ,","depth":13},{"id":221,"text":"but there were no questions","depth":14},{"id":222,"text":"about whether Sessions relayed Comey ' s concerns to anyone , such as other Justice Department officials or the White House counsel .","depth":14},{"id":223,"text":"Sessions said","depth":13},{"id":224,"text":"Comey could have brought the concerns to others","depth":14},{"id":225,"text":"but never said","depth":15},{"id":226,"text":"he suggested any such action .","depth":15},{"id":227,"text":"Another potential layup might have been to ask Sessions","depth":12},{"id":228,"text":"whether he considers Comey a \" nut job \" or \" crazy \"","depth":13},{"id":229,"text":"- as Trump reportedly said in a meeting with Russian officials","depth":14},{"id":230,"text":"just a day after sacking the FBI director .","depth":14}],"relations":[{"parent":461,"left":268,"right":460,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":237,"right":267,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":235,"right":236,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":235,"left":0,"right":234,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":232,"right":233,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":232,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":241,"right":266,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":7,"right":240,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":240,"left":8,"right":239,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":239,"left":9,"right":238,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":238,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":254,"right":265,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":254,"left":247,"right":253,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":2